Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說你啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你最近上課的時候太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我好好反省
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼放學之後去打掃實驗室的事情就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:27.00,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\pos(866,332)\frz350.3}教職工會議 筆記
