Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.00,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\frz343.1\pos(1118,496)}打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:24.79,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\frz343.1\pos(1394,584)}本班負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.00,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\frz343.1\pos(1394,584)}本班負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,桌子也要擦乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,輪班打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,憑什麼只罰我一個人打掃衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明高木同學也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都怪她整天在上課時捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我的反應是很吵沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,趕緊弄完回家吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被我嚇到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 一動不動地在這裡等著也算值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也被罰搞衛生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,趕緊打掃乾淨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:51.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然要搞衛生 用遊戲的方式來做會更好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:59.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,輸的那個要打掃教室的四分之一 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說 只要贏四次就不用幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 那先是第一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 沒想到她竟然宣告了自己要出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那準備了哦 首先是石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼只要出布 我就能贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都說了要出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一次就相信高木同學的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:38.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 順帶一提 我不再說自己要出什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:47.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 難道又被她捉弄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們倆在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,上課太吵被老師罰打掃這裡的衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那還真是要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那中井你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:11.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,隨便逛逛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井 不要打擾人家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 你是說打掃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啦 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 高木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:40.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:41.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛的那兩個人在交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會吧 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然覺得他們總待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有藏著掖著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過他們是不會主動說出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說是隨便逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:06.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該是要去天台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,天台？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:12.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們現在肯定在天台獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,獨處…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有在打掃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,兩人獨處 很青春嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,青春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,結果四次都輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,終於弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你要是真的吸取教訓的話就不要捉弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放心吧 捉弄你的時候我會更收斂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不怕再被老師罰搞衛生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個嘛 船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 老師也沒有罰我來打掃課室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼每次被老師罵的都只有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 你又是為了捉弄我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 那也算一個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也想青春一把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:06.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,青…青春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 回家路上請我喝果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻單槓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 要不要賭上飲料來場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,至於比賽的內容 可以讓我來決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,單槓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:46.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在高的那一邊翻單槓 做不到就算輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:52.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 最近在高的那邊練習了無數次翻單槓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,終於成功地翻上了平生第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:00.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自那以後 我就一直等著和高木同學比這個的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然高木同學也有可能成功地翻上單槓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:11.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片 我今天穿的是裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,穿著裙子就做不了翻單槓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就沒辦法和我對決了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我先開始可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:32.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 我翻單槓的時候 你要面向另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說 我穿的可是裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:40.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是在我翻單槓的時候轉頭 就算西片輸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了 下一個 輪到西片了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的 她真的翻上單槓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不要再想多餘的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,兩個人都成功了呢 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼又輪到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然想都不想地答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這麼從容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道她就不怕下次翻不過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實她沒翻單槓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:42.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然說看向那邊算我輸 但作弊就要另當別論了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:45.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我一定要戰勝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可能 她在翻單槓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,短褲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 可以轉過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天西片主動認輸了 沒什麼贏的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:41.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說 既然你穿了短褲 我不把頭轉過去也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你好色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:00.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我是為了確認你有沒有在翻單槓才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:06.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那西片是認為我會耍小花招嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個嘛…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.94,Takagisan-text2,,0,0,0,,{\fs300\pos(1406,428)}單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.94,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\frz31.87\pos(1076,218)}100％
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.94,Takagisan-text3,,0,0,0,,{\fs200\frz346.6\pos(1836,460)}♥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 他究竟怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:34.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,整天要管我閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 你並不討厭我這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 你並不討厭我這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,百分百單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聽好了 我已經說過好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:20.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這部分考試會考到 記住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是西片啊 你今天不是感冒請假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是的 沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 你感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是什麼大不了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,決定性的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道你熬夜看百分百單相思了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼她會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 你聲音太大了高木同…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聲音大的是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:30.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 明明我還生著病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,捉弄起來一點也不含糊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:42.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 今天的我準備了一條秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你這個外人會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:50.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我生氣了 我一定要跟那個人好好抱怨一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這一招能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:20.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然感冒了，但和學到的新姿勢比起來不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,儘管捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的回擊會把你羞得面紅耳赤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放馬過來吧 什麼時候我都奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 為什麼沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一直擺著這個姿勢也挺累的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且還做不了筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 是這個姿勢暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了我想要反擊的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把姿勢放自然一點怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你到底怎麼了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放在平時  這段時間足夠你捉弄我三次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道她也感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:59.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一言不發的高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:23.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺回擊用的那句「你真可愛」突然就變得很羞恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:29.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 那種話根本就說不出口吧 我是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:32.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,熬夜導致的睡眠不足和感冒弄得我腦子都不太正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的臉有點紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 不難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是你的臉很紅 有發熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼今天會那麼溫柔啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 真的沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如說感冒其實只是個藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,起床的時候已經是八點半 所以才遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以真的沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你其實很健康嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 我可以捉弄你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:20.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,結果 這一天比平時被捉弄的次數還要多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 由加莉 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要為了一根冰棍急匆匆的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為那可是烤番薯味的冰棍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是夏季限定的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,夏天吃烤番薯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論哪裡都賣完了 我猜粗點心店還會剩一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以動作快一點 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明我們挑了條捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學和西片在粗點心店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那兩人難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 不要打擾他們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 高木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,買到了 烤番薯味的冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你問什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那當然是…男女之間的關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:44.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你沒看到嗎 明明是你自己設的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 為什麼要跟著那兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這和回去的路是兩個方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,噓 被發現了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起這個 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看著那兩個人 你們有沒有什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明有自行車 可以兩個人一起騎回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好啊 兩人一起騎自行車回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:19.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是走路的話兩人獨處的時候會更長 真讓人為難呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是自行車爆胎了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我吃一口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只能吃一口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 要不要來比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 過了前面的路口就開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,先到神社的人為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 高木同學的自行車爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是我跑得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們肯定不會聊這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來比賽算什麼啊 比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是在聊些更曖昧的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然比誰先到神社也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會不會是已經到神社了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說跟蹤暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回去再買一根冰棍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我吃一口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她們走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們會被跟蹤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:08.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 我們走快一點 到下一個路口轉彎不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 明明這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這麼一說 還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:18.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片覺得那樣比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 其實怎麼樣都無所謂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:29.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 我們不是還要比誰先到神社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:31.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,預備 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:38.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我等等 你這是搶跑 高木同學
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,————ed————
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:14.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 感覺跟蹤別人也挺好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:16.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,白白繞了一圈遠路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然還是被他們發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:22.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天得向高木同學道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:27.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,烤番薯味冰棍賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過沒關係 還有紅豆年糕湯味的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你能不能重視一下應季的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我吃一口
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.97,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:36.39,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:46.73,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:55.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:01:03.83,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:12.17,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:16.05,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.97,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:28.06,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:36.36,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:41.78,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:56.01,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
