Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:22.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你挽著我的手臂 輕聲呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:31.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「再陪我一會兒 再陪我一會兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:43.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}我要把這思念傳達給你 在世界被染上黑暗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:51.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以拜託了 請留在我身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}因為我是如此地愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:59.02,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}願這思念能傳達到你的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:04.48,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}希望這一切都能化為現實
